- [ ] TestDb factory creates isolated databases
- [ ] Fixtures provide realistic test data
- [ ] E2E script runs all critical scenarios
- [ ] CI workflow runs on relevant changes
- [ ] All tests produce detailed logs on failure
- [ ] Tests clean up after themselves (temp directories removed)
- [ ] Performance tests have defined thresholds
- [ ] Tests can run in parallel without interference

## Dependencies

This bead has NO dependencies - it provides infrastructure for other beads.

